title: Drakan: The Ancients' Gates Playthrough â€” Part 5
description: Holy cow this is a long session. Wasn't planning on finishing the game today, but that's what happened. I was actually having a lot of fun so time just kind of slipped by. Really fun game, although unfortunately very repetitive. Especially the combat, it really never changes through out the whole game and is kind of dull, but it's not so bad that it's painful to play. Glad to say I've finally finished this game.
